{"tid":1744410,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「撐香港!要自由演唱會」周五將加碼於台南花園夜市舉辦","createTime":"2019-11-21T16:59:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T21:28:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2cbd1b1ba057531d914c016d73694964a128db4a","tid":1744410,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T16:59:21.000Z","msg":"《願榮光歸香港》萬人合唱台語版 網友深夜重播「聽一次哭一次」<br />\n<br />\n週日(11/17)晚間在自由廣場舉辦的「撐香港!要自由演唱會」吸引逾兩萬民眾參與。演唱會兩波高潮，不僅有滅火器開場演唱由林夕填詞，獻給香港的歌曲《雙城記》，演唱會壓軸，董事長樂團更與管樂團、合唱團大編制演出台語版《願榮光歸香港》，並邀請全場民眾一起大合唱。主辦單位19號深夜於「撐！自由 Freedom is not Free」臉書粉絲專頁公佈「願榮光歸香港-台語版」MV，記錄萬人共同演唱力挺香港的動人時刻，並搭配反送中運動的經典畫面，台灣做伙挺香港！震撼感人！<br />\n<br />\n「黎明來到欲光復我們的香港，眾人兒女為正義時代革命。」台灣萬人合唱台語版《願榮光歸香港》MV影片推出後，已破萬人觀看，許多網友都大受感動，紛紛在深夜分享道：「突然醒來突然睡不著」、「聽一次哭一次」、「天佑香港、香港加油」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》粵語版，在香港反送中抗爭場合中被廣為流傳，為最具有指標性的歌曲，先前網路上不僅有網友自發創作管弦樂及合唱團版、手語版MV，如今主辦單位也剪輯「撐香港!要自由演唱會」中，由董事長樂團X董事長合唱團X彩虹城市管樂團演出，與民眾共同演唱的「台語版」，畫面不僅記錄當晚台下民眾頭掛布條、手舉加油扇、打開手機燈光，將自由廣場點城萬人燈海的壯觀景象，自由廣場牌樓上更投影著大大「自由香港、FREE HK」字樣，為港人打氣，演唱畢，全場更齊聲吶喊「光復香港、時代革命，沒有暴徒、只有暴政，香港人加油、台灣人加油」等口號，要讓香港民眾聽見台灣人「Stand with Hong Kong」的信念。<br />\n<br />\n為了持續聲援香港反送中，「撐香港!要自由演唱會」本周五將加碼於台南花園夜市舉辦，由董事長樂團、朱頭皮、陳明章、槍擊潑辣、謝銘祐等音樂人，持續用音樂的力量，撐香港的自由。"},{"pid":"8ab54d8fe89f59501e4cb710e12f94c3168e88fb","tid":1744410,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T16:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3982f850e112257570e369c82323e9ec1d268ac7","tid":1744410,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T17:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d07f2a4187262dbc102ee9b36b1050d70360b8","tid":1744410,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T17:04:02.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"fca7be9b6ed04f0c6db2bba15b86e018f3510686","tid":1744410,"uid":20272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T17:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e62b3999b483249efe4ea7ffd76c994b6251d70b","tid":1744410,"uid":184985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T17:13:24.000Z","msg":"感動<br />\n香港都有就好"},{"pid":"669fae25aa94f25c0b5037299e71e544098ca26d","tid":1744410,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T17:32:06.000Z","msg":"1117臺北場已經有兩萬人參與咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a81c23057dd59b8e84c07bf4d2ac79a8fbddc2","tid":1744410,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T21:28:44.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}